 Sources have initimated to Citizen Digital that Muturi, who is the leader of the Democratic Party will sign an agreement with Kenya Kwanza on Saturday morning in Nairobi. Muturi previously declared that he is eyeing the presidential seat in the upcoming August General Election. The National Assembly Speaker will become the latest key Mt. Kenya leader to join the DP Ruto led political alliance. Saturday marks the deadline for political coalition parties to submit their agreementsÂ  to the Registrar of Political Parties as per the Political Parties (Amendment) Act 2021.